\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2FIMG_2690.jpg&h=3e278a31&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/23/IMG_2691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2FIMG_2691.jpg&h=f28d8aaf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/23/IMG_2695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2FIMG_2695.jpg&h=76c78455&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/23/IMG_2697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2FIMG_2697.jpg&h=34e28328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔使去淘寶，唔使去深水埗 <br />\n唔使去咖啡店，唔使過新都會 <br />\n快d去新葵芳花園休憩地方休息，做0下運動 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/23/IMG_2705.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2FIMG_2705.jpg&h=35a65930&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/23/IMG_2706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2FIMG_2706.jpg&h=bb295ed3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/23/IMG_2707.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2FIMG_2707.jpg&h=77835e4d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/23/IMG_2708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2FIMG_2708.jpg&h=aea34ce1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/23/IMG_2719.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2FIMG_2719.jpg&h=7572583c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/23/IMG_2721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2FIMG_2721.jpg&h=9f1a7f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/23/IMG_2718.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2FIMG_2718.jpg&h=b9d858a2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/23/IMG_2722.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2FIMG_2722.jpg&h=119578af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9a6d6bf4b40daa6c3bfac939f60addd10327b56","tid":51336,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:47:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20150130/19022617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20150130%2F19022617&d=F%2BAJnKwjjw8KxF%2BwFnr1zQv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=e18a4fe5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20150130%2F19022617&h=2801fb76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20150130/19022617</a> <br />\n<br />\n審計報告指私人發展商管理公共空間的問題，例如是關閘、暫停服務的升降機、以花盆阻路，及「私人地方」指示牌等等，防礙公眾使用公共空間。位於新葵芳花園，佔地約6400平方米的休憩公園，市民需經過屋苑大堂才可到達，但屋苑前則張貼了「私人地方，閒人免進」指示牌。附近居民胡先生並不知情，亦從未內進休憩，得知是公共空間時感驚訝。他指應增設指示牌於當眼處，以便大眾使用，「我知道後會多進去」。 <br />\n<br />\n自2008年時代廣場前空地，被揭發屬於所有人都可以免費及自由使用的公共空間後，引起了大眾對公共空間的關注。故政府於2011年制定一份《私人發展公眾休憩空間設計及管理指引》，指示發展商妥善管理。誠然，這份指引並沒有法律約束力，發展商可以不理會，繼續以自定的管理方法，私有公共空間。 <br />\n<br />\n這個對發展商有利的政策安排是源於1980年，政府將一些公共設施，如巴士站，公眾休憩地方等等，安排在私人發展項目內，讓發展商增加地積比，目的是促進當年的私人及城市發展。公共專業聯盟黎廣德指摘政府將提供公共空間的責任推給發展商，「當初在賣地或者規劃時，其實是政府『縮骨』。從公眾的角度來說，某些私人管理的公共空間，是市民付了錢(稅)去買公共空間，只不過是付錢(稅)後用不到，這是最可笑的地方。」他認為政府多年來並沒有誠意還地於民。 <br />\n<br />\n政府表示不再鼓勵於私人地方設立公共空間，以平息公眾的情緒。然而，現時私人管理公眾空間的問題，仍然未解決。"},{"pid":"c8b16a19a9b9e5e9d3a4035a478c589237702f50","tid":51336,"uid":35941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc4813fb84818284132ef66aa930bcce03661c0","tid":51336,"uid":51446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"睇標題仲以為想講 葵涌公園"},{"pid":"0e2624c54b61ef542e6db3f634549f67e8853294","tid":51336,"uid":25141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:51:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04bb99f66187790b6071a2540ffce94d0a8a6d83","tid":51336,"uid":65335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:52:53.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"27e4044fe1a02dc98ba1ee1216554cfe224c8a4e","tid":51336,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec30828f29be7d1517225d748f26801382c97e2","tid":51336,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"屌，一定要去踩場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n火燃滾<br />\n咁多空間，我上去曬太陽、睇書、聽歌<br />\n好過出街鳩行shopping centre"},{"pid":"5e65ccc676a9477b64dadc14eda317266e428b17","tid":51336,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:57:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe715d766ad4a0caeaf8d65ebbfa73a4b808a34e","tid":51336,"uid":30412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:03:49.000Z","msg":"東區有冇依啲地方"},{"pid":"3a8b1b50ed5c392edcb30a80b8730b577c7ad375","tid":51336,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:07:01.000Z","msg":"日頭會比實Q趕"},{"pid":"1f2c6af4205f720ce52b6b3438a27c3f8e4e4138","tid":51336,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy